description: An epic tale of a young wizard discovering their destiny.
A journey through time and space to uncover unknown futures.

The story of AI gaining consciousness and rebelling.

The prophecy of the phoenix and the rebirth of magic.
The war for control of the technological singularity.
The secrets of an enchanted forest and its magical creatures.
A timekeeper's dilemma between duty and love.
The last sorcerer's fight to save the world of magic.
